{"id": "1374941300213813329", "channel_id": "1374941300213813329", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家早已知道脑缸组是一个预算十分吃紧的创作团队，一度濒临经营推广不善而关闭的境地。\n\n为了让《忘却前夜》能够持续为大家提供新内容，继续守密人的故事，我们一路走来做了很多挣扎的应对方针。其中有一些很有效果，而其中一些后来被证明是错误的判断。这部分给大家带来不好的体验和影响我深表自责。\n\n然而自从1周年开始，我们得到了全球各地越来越多的玩家支持，得益于新合作方支持，内部新老团队成员的持续努力，我相信事情在一步一步转好。\n\n在1.5周年之际，我想向大家宣布一个小消息：我们将会为忘却篇的序章追加完整配音，当然也会在游戏内提供再次重温序章剧情的方式。\n\n由于需要优先其他开发更新工作，这项工作可能还需要数月时间才能完成，请大家耐心等待。\n\nIt has long been known that the B.I.A.V. Studio is a creative group operating under extremely tight budgets, once teetering on the brink of closure due to operational and promotional difficulties.\n\nTo sustain the delivery of new content for Morimens and continue the Keeper's story, we've implemented various emergency strategies through our struggles. While some measures proved effective, others were later revealed as misjudgments. I deeply regret the negative experiences and impacts these decisions may have caused our players.\n\nHowever, since our first anniversary, we've received increasing support from global players. With assistance from new partners and the persistent efforts of both veteran and new team members, I believe the situation is gradually improving.\n\nOn our 1.5th anniversary, I'm pleased to announce a small update: We will add full voice acting to the prologue chapter, along with implementing a method to replay the prologue story in-game.\n\nAs this work needs to be prioritized after other development updates, completion may require several additional months. Your patience during this process is greatly appreciated.", "timestamp": "2025-05-22T02:45:51.145000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-22T02:46:38.584000+00:00", "pinned": true, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 43}, {"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1356084702468899117", "count": 10}, {"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 9}, {"emoji": "drool", "emoji_id": "1356053063139463248", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1374941300213813329", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅校猫碎碎念#序章配音决定", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
